 Basic Cookbook<\/i> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe.","Serve curry with a side of cooked rice and Naan bread if desired.","<strong>Vegan pulse and pumpkin curry:<\/strong> omit the yoghurt to serve."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","6 portions"]}